claim.claim-text:
30. An oven comprising:
a housing defining a baking chamber and a baking chamber opening, said baking chamber opening having a width dimension and a height dimension, wherein the width dimension is greater than the height dimension, and wherein said baking chamber opening is of sufficient size to allow a baking item to pass therethrough;
a circular metal pan disposed within the baking chamber, said metal pan having a plurality of openings provided about a central axis wherein said central axis extends in a direction that is substantially parallel to the height dimension of the baking chamber opening;
a baking stone supported by said metal pan;
a gas-powered infrared burner disposed within the baking chamber below the circular metal pan; and
a motor operatively connected to the circular metal pan, said motor adapted to rotate the circular metal pan about the central axis.
